      <div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://reviewsindepth.com/2010/11/the-social-network-the-end-of-intimacy-and-the-birth-of-hacker-sensibility/comment-page-1/#comment-244">December 7, 2010 at 11:34 pm</a></div>

      <p>wow you can sure type a story, nice one.</p>

      <div class="reply">
         <a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2010/11/the-social-network-the-end-of-intimacy-and-the-birth-of-hacker-sensibility/?replytocom=244#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-244", "244", "respond", "2569")'>Reply</a>      </div>
