         <cite class="fn"><a href="http://dudeart.tumblr.com" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-commentauthor','http://dudeart.tumblr.com']);"  rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Dudarte</a></cite> <span class="says">says:</span>      </div>
      
      <div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://reviewsindepth.com/2010/11/the-social-network-the-end-of-intimacy-and-the-birth-of-hacker-sensibility/comment-page-1/#comment-674">March 11, 2011 at 12:06 am</a></div>

      <p>Sorry, wrong website link! :/</p>

      <div class="reply">
         <a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2010/11/the-social-network-the-end-of-intimacy-and-the-birth-of-hacker-sensibility/?replytocom=674#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-674", "674", "respond", "2569")'>Reply</a>      </div>
