      <p>Are you concerned that most people mature enough to appreciate the brilliance of your essay will remain too self-interested to pursue any legitimately altruistic goals?</p>

      <div class="reply">
         <a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2010/11/the-social-network-the-end-of-intimacy-and-the-birth-of-hacker-sensibility/?replytocom=715#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-715", "715", "respond", "2569")'>Reply</a>      </div>
