         <a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2010/11/the-social-network-the-end-of-intimacy-and-the-birth-of-hacker-sensibility/?replytocom=716#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-716", "716", "respond", "2569")'>Reply</a>      </div>
