      <p>Apologies Dieter &#8211; I meant to reply to your comment quite a while ago but it just got away from me.</p>
<p>Big fan of the Adam Curtis documentaries &#8211; and have been strongly influenced by them (I have a review of one of them on this site).</p>
<p>After your comment I am actually amazed that it didn&#8217;t occur to me to consider the issue of online dating and porn &#8211; it&#8217;s such an interesting one so I thank you for bringing it up.  But yeah &#8211; the essay was probably too long already.  If you know of any good resources on the matter &#8211; feel free to post them here.</p>

